The paper discusses the challenges of capturing engagement on Facebook for altmetrics, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL), social media (cs.SOC), and cyber security (cs.CYBER). The paper also involves querying and mapping URLs, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and web science (cs.WEB). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of Facebook for sharing academic content, which is related to social informatics (cs.SI).
